Actress Nkechi Sunday has slammed a fan who tattooed her name on her hand. The actress, who wondered if there’s a new trend of fans tattooing the names of celebrities they love, told her fan that she is on her own and not getting more than the appreciation post she shared. Nkechi Blessing Sunday tweeted: ‘’Na the new trend be this? Aunty Oyinda I just hope those ain’t permanent tattoo..Cus OYO Le wa oooo. me sef Dey find who to draw wey go dash me small thing..I love you ooo but you ain’t getting more than this very post I no Dey claim wetin I no be..IRE ooooo.”  